        {
            "title": "全日收市︱持續調整 恒指跌32點報22944點 芯片股氣勢勁 恒生績後受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後持續調整，主板成交進一步縮至2625.67億元。芯片股氣勢如虹，業績股表現暫較遜色，恒生(00011)更成藍籌包尾。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數經過昨天於23000點得而復失後，今早低開199點後初段進一步尋底，跌幅曾擴大至327點，低見22649點，其後迅速由谷底反彈，中段跌幅一度收窄至僅跌1點，衝上22975點，只是暫欠再彈動力，其後大部份時間在跌幅約210點以內徘徊；恒指最後收報22944點，跌32點或0.14%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數繼續跑贏大市，今早開市後約45分鐘已開始倒升，其後進入好淡爭持局面，收報5672點，升33點或0.59%；國企指數則跌12點或0.15%，報8463點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14717961-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e6%8c%81%e7%ba%8c%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c32%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b122944%e9%bb%9e-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e6%b0%a3%e5%8b%a2%e5%8b%81",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 16:20:52",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
    ]
